  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Jesucristo sumaj Michejniy
 Cheqan ñampi purichiwan./
 
[V2]
 /Tukuy juchata saqeniña,
 K'anchaynimpitaj purini./
 
[V3]
 /Kay pachapi k'anchawampuni,
 Cristo jesús qhuyawajniy./
 
[V4]
 /Juchapi chinkasqa kawsaqe,
 Cristoman jamullawajña. /
 
[V5]
 /Jesucristoman qayllajtiyki,
 Juchaykita pampachanqa./
 
</lyrics></song>